    Body: 'So Voytsekh sent you south. Good. Walk with open eyes: black slime, torn
      reeds, tracks too heavy for a man.'
    Choices:
    - Text: I took the contract. What should I look for?
      NextNodeId: tracks
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: marta_spoken
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Why does the swamp remember the dead?
      NextNodeId: curse
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Later.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: tracks
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: Look for claw cuts, poisoned slime, and cloth caught on the reeds. When
      all three agree, draw silver.
    Choices:
    - Text: Then I start with the tracks.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
    - Text: Tell me about the curse.
      NextNodeId: curse
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
  - Id: curse
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: People blame Elsa because a single witch is easier than a village full
      of liars. Survive the monster first; truth comes later.
    Choices:
    - Text: I will inspect the swamp.
      NextNodeId: tracks
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: marta_spoken
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Enough for now.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
